User Guide
1) The SimonSays game begins by displaying all the four colors on the scene. 
2) A pattern is then flashed on the buttons in a random order.
3) The user then has to select the colors that match the flashed pattern.
Note: If a mistake is made they will have to start over again. 
4) After the correct order is inputted, the game continues with an additional randomly generated color to be flashed in the sequence.
5) The user will continue to match the flashed color pattern. If they do not follow the correct order the game will end.
